org.elasticsearch.common.settings

Class Setting<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.elasticsearch.action.support.ToXContentToBytes
      • org.elasticsearch.common.settings.Setting<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ToXContent

    public class Setting<T>
extends ToXContentToBytes
    A setting. Encapsulates typical stuff like default value, parsing, and scope. Some (dynamic=true) can by modified at run time using the API.

    • Nested Class Summary

        dynamic - true iff this setting can be dynamically updateable
        scope - the scope of this setting

      • get

        public T get(Settings settings)

      • getRaw

        public java.lang.String getRaw(Settings settings)
        Returns the raw (string) settings value. If the setting is not present in the given settings object the default value is returned instead. This is useful if the value can't be parsed due to an invalid value to access the actual value.

      • match
